1
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:13,959
What's wrong?

2
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:17,879
You look so calm.

3
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,959
This pearl must be fake.

4
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:21,079
Every time I passed out,

5
00:01:21,079 --> 00:01:22,439
it meant the pearl was real.

6
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:24,359
But you can't really say that.

7
00:01:24,599 --> 00:01:26,760
But you did pass out back in Yunling.

8
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:29,159
Every time you held this pearl,

9
00:01:29,159 --> 00:01:30,719
your face would contort.

10
00:01:30,719 --> 00:01:31,560
And all that crazy stuff.

11
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:32,959
You're so calm this time,

12
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:37,079
which means this divine pearl has no magic.

13
00:01:37,159 --> 00:01:38,000
Alright, alright.

14
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,480
What divine pearl?

15
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,040
You're just talking superstitious nonsense.

16
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:42,480
Bro,

17
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:44,879
how about we take this pearl abroad?

18
00:01:45,079 --> 00:01:46,359
The archaeology department at my school

19
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:48,719
has a team studying such mysterious antiques.

20
00:01:49,239 --> 00:01:50,200
No way.

21
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,480
This is a Chinese artifact.

22
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:53,760
How can it go abroad?

23
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:55,079
That's losing our national treasures.

24
00:02:02,599 --> 00:02:03,480
We were too busy celebrating.

25
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:05,719
We forgot we're sitting on a volcano.

26
00:02:05,959 --> 00:02:06,920
Anyway, we've got the pearl.

27
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:07,799
Let's go.

28
00:02:07,799 --> 00:02:08,479
Right, right.

29
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,400
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

30
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:12,719
Darn it!

31
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:14,479
Look, the tree sap is melting.

32
00:02:14,599 --> 00:02:15,520
The tree hole will be sealed shut.

33
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,159
Everyone, let's go! Hurry!

34
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:17,080
Go, go, go! Careful, careful!

35
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:18,080
Go, go, go! Hurry!

36
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,439
Commander Chen, help!

37
00:02:30,479 --> 00:02:31,280
I can't get out!

38
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,400
Pull hard!

39
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:40,759
Alright, alright.

40
00:02:41,919 --> 00:02:42,560
Hurry up!

41
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:58,960
Chen Youxi!

42
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:01,479
Lao Lu, watch out!

43
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,159
Wh-What do we do, Lao Chen?

44
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:19,479
Bro!

45
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:20,879
The ground is cracking again!

46
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,400
The magma is exposed!

47
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,719
Listen to me.

48
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:24,800
I'll take the lead.

49
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,039
You all follow.

50
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,360
Don't wander off.

51
00:03:27,879 --> 00:03:28,800
If I fall in,

52
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,000
keep moving forward.

53
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,479
Whoever can make it out, make it out.

54
00:03:31,479 --> 00:03:31,919
Pfft!

55
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:32,960
Don't jinx it!

56
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,560
What do you mean "whoever can make it out"?

57
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,919
We leave together!

58
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:37,680
Fatty!

59
00:03:38,719 --> 00:03:39,759
Okay, okay, okay.

60
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:40,879
We'll listen to you.

61
00:03:40,879 --> 00:03:41,520
Let's go!

62
00:03:45,199 --> 00:03:45,840
Lao Lu!

63
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,000
Dawei!

64
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:52,439
Come on!

65
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,719
Hurry! Hurry up!

66
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,199
Come on!

67
00:03:58,479 --> 00:03:59,439
Dawei, jump!

68
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,120
Jump, Dawei!

69
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,159
Jump! Hurry!

70
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:05,840
Just close your eyes and jump! Hurry up!

71
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:06,439
Come on!

72
00:04:07,319 --> 00:04:08,080
Hurry!

73
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:09,759
Give me your hand!

74
00:04:10,199 --> 00:04:11,199
Jump! Come on!

75
00:04:11,199 --> 00:04:12,199
Dawei, jump!

76
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:22,040
Go! Slow down, slow down.

77
00:04:22,319 --> 00:04:22,839
Hurry!

78
00:04:30,399 --> 00:04:31,319
Oh my god.

79
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,279
Alright, alright.

80
00:04:37,519 --> 00:04:39,720
I wonder if this Lingxiao Pearl

81
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,759
can lift the curse on Lao Chen.

82
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:44,439
Why worry about that now?

83
00:04:44,639 --> 00:04:45,720
Let's just hold onto it.

84
00:04:45,959 --> 00:04:47,319
We still have Director Zhu, right?

85
00:04:47,319 --> 00:04:48,160
Right. When we get back,

86
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,720
we can ask around together.

87
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:50,560
Right, right, right.

88
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:54,639
Do you guys remember the murals in the tomb passage?

89
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,920
You mean the ritual?

90
00:04:57,439 --> 00:04:58,040
Yes.

91
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:02,040
The mural showed abnormal weather,

92
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:03,680
and people being swept into the air.

93
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,560
We all thought it was a natural phenomenon.

94
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,759
But we overlooked a detail.

95
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,920
The ground beneath the high priest's feet

96
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,279
actually had cracks.

97
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,399
At the time, Lao Chen thought

98
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,920
they were marks left by time.

99
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,560
So no one paid attention to it.

100
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:17,480
Sis,

101
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,720
are you trying to say

102
00:05:18,839 --> 00:05:20,199
that the year recorded on the mural

103
00:05:20,199 --> 00:05:20,959
is the year when Guyu

104
00:05:20,959 --> 00:05:22,439
experienced crustal movement?

105
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:23,399
Yes.

106
00:05:24,519 --> 00:05:26,399
The King of Dian had been waiting for the right time to ascend.

107
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:28,720
But besides the Lingxiao Pearl, the ritual

108
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,480
also required a celestial anomaly.

109
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,160
In modern terms,

110
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,920
it should be a volcanic eruption.

111
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,560
The few times recorded in Guyu

112
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:40,120
probably only involved crustal movement.

113
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,360
The volcano didn't actually erupt.

114
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:44,040
That's why this information has been passed down.

115
00:05:45,519 --> 00:05:46,120
They wanted to wait until

116
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,720
the day the volcano truly erupted,

117
00:05:47,959 --> 00:05:50,720
so descendants could use the Lingxiao Pearl to complete the ritual.

118
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:54,439
Then...

119
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:57,560
Then didn't we arrive at the exact right time?

120
00:05:57,959 --> 00:05:59,160
That's easy then.

121
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,879
Isn't the altar right over there?

122
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,839
We'll know once we go over and take a look.

123
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:06,759
Let's go.

124
00:06:07,279 --> 00:06:07,839
Let's go.

125
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,439
Hurry! Hurry!

126
00:06:26,879 --> 00:06:27,360
Lao Lu!

127
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,360
Lao Lu, hurry!

128
00:06:29,279 --> 00:06:29,759
Come on!

129
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,120
Lao Lu!

130
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:32,160
Jump!

131
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:32,800
Come on!

132
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,600
No, Bro, Bro!

133
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,319
It's on fire!

134
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:41,279
Fire, fire, fire!

135
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,199
I'll treat you to a meal when we get back.

136
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,639
Commander Chen is treating.

137
00:06:48,639 --> 00:06:49,519
That's rare.

138
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:50,480
Mutton hotpot.

139
00:06:50,839 --> 00:06:51,639
I'm treating.

140
00:06:51,879 --> 00:06:52,800
Lao Lu is paying.

141
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,480
Then we'll have to eat for three days straight.

142
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,560
Aren't you afraid of overeating?

143
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,639
What about you, Shutong?

144
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,560
Me?

145
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,519
Wait until we get back safely.

146
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:02,600
What you owe me,

147
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:04,040
I'll settle the score with you then.

148
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,120
Commander Chen,

149
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:07,000
I think the rest of your life is spoken for.

150
00:07:07,519 --> 00:07:08,160
Watch out!

151
00:07:11,879 --> 00:07:13,720
Why is there another big gap here?

152
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:15,560
We can't cross it this time.

153
00:07:17,959 --> 00:07:19,959
Here's the plan. I'll jump over first.

154
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,680
I'll pull you over with the grappling hook.

155
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:34,279
Dawei, you go first.

156
00:07:39,399 --> 00:07:40,360
Jump hard!

157
00:07:51,519 --> 00:07:52,879
Come on, come on!

158
00:07:55,399 --> 00:07:56,600
Lao Lu, come over!

159
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,480
One, two, three!

160
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:05,920
Mr. Lu!

161
00:08:12,639 --> 00:08:14,319
Fatty, jump over quickly!

162
00:08:14,399 --> 00:08:15,920
Advisor He, there's no time!

163
00:08:15,959 --> 00:08:16,560
Jump!

164
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:19,680
Come on!

165
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,000
One, two, three, go!

166
00:10:23,919 --> 00:10:24,440
Bro.

167
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:26,879
Half of the Lingxiao Pearl is mine, and half is yours.

168
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,720
No matter what we see or hear,

169
00:10:28,799 --> 00:10:30,039
we split it equally, okay?

170
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:39,679
Bro,

171
00:10:39,759 --> 00:10:40,919
as long as we go to the altar now,

172
00:10:40,919 --> 00:10:42,919
we can explore the mysteries of the entire universe.

173
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:44,480
You don't need to throw your life away

174
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:45,840
for a few other people.

175
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:48,240
I'm taking the Lingxiao Pearl to break the curse

176
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:49,960
just to spend a few more years with them.

177
00:10:50,279 --> 00:10:51,600
To hell with your universe!

178
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,360
Bro, Bro!

179
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,039
We are not enemies.

180
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,799
You really don't have to do this.

181
00:11:07,559 --> 00:11:08,840
If you want this pearl,

182
00:11:09,559 --> 00:11:10,879
you just have to ask me for it.

183
00:11:12,399 --> 00:11:13,000
Bro,

184
00:11:13,679 --> 00:11:15,000
if it were just you,

185
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:17,080
I definitely would have asked you for it.

186
00:11:17,399 --> 00:11:19,039
But those three are different from you.

187
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:21,360
They came for you.

188
00:11:21,399 --> 00:11:23,399
How could they possibly give me the pearl?

189
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,440
So you killed people?

190
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,960
You killed people?!

191
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:29,559
Bro,

192
00:11:30,159 --> 00:11:31,679
I had no other choice!

193
00:11:32,039 --> 00:11:33,120
But for the Lingxiao Pearl,

194
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,639
I had to do it.

195
00:11:46,519 --> 00:11:47,679
What exactly do you want?

196
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,440
Do you know Bai Lingling?

197
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:52,519
I'm in the same organization as her.

198
00:11:55,399 --> 00:11:56,399
Our boss

199
00:11:57,120 --> 00:12:00,600
has been collecting Lingxiao Pearls from all over the world.

200
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:03,480
They say it's to break the curse.

201
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:05,799
But I eavesdropped.

202
00:12:06,159 --> 00:12:07,720
It's not just that.

203
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,399
It's said that this Lingxiao Pearl

204
00:12:09,759 --> 00:12:11,759
hides secrets about the universe.

205
00:12:12,679 --> 00:12:13,879
Whoever gets it

206
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:16,799
can control the whole world.

207
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,200
Crazy.

208
00:12:19,279 --> 00:12:20,519
You're all crazy.

209
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:23,799
You guys are smart, though.

210
00:12:24,519 --> 00:12:27,759
You knew to lure people to Fucheng.

211
00:12:28,159 --> 00:12:29,080
But you overlooked

212
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:30,720
how well Bai Lingling knows you.

213
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,639
From the moment Director Zhu left the provincial capital

214
00:12:33,639 --> 00:12:35,840
to look for you in Nanyun,

215
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:38,320
he was targeted by our people.

216
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,000
As soon as you arrived in Jinghong,

217
00:12:43,279 --> 00:12:44,519
the organization sent me.

218
00:12:55,799 --> 00:12:56,440
Bro,

219
00:12:57,320 --> 00:13:00,320
I'm not the main culprit behind all this.

220
00:13:02,639 --> 00:13:04,039
Give me the Lingxiao Pearl,

221
00:13:05,039 --> 00:13:06,440
and I'll take you to the organization

222
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,120
to get revenge on the boss.

223
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:40,679
Bro.

224
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,480
Should I give you a hand,

225
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,759
or will you die on your own?

226
00:13:44,799 --> 00:13:46,320
For the sake of our past friendship,

227
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,519
I'll give you a hand.

228
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:02,159
The world is so beautiful.

229
00:14:10,759 --> 00:14:11,440
Bro.

230
00:14:11,919 --> 00:14:13,440
For the sake of our friendship,

231
00:14:13,679 --> 00:14:15,039
I'll let you enjoy the view for a while.

232
00:14:15,519 --> 00:14:16,679
Bye-bye.

233
00:15:26,879 --> 00:15:28,000
Fatty was right.

234
00:15:28,919 --> 00:15:30,720
Evil knows no age.

235
00:15:32,519 --> 00:15:34,600
I can't believe I didn't trust my brother,

236
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,080
and trusted you instead.
